entries.femaleVariant: Spoke with Miguel. Valentinos've accepted our terms.
And Stevenson? He gonna give us the code to the cell? Almost got busted last time.
Key word – "almost." Could've happened to anyone.
Luckily, Stevenson gives second chances. Besides, if everything goes smoothly, he gets a nice, juicy cut.
Still – if we get caught with our dicks out, we're on our own. His hands'll be clean.
Yeah, never misses an opportunity to make that clear.
